text:
When doing in apache2.conf for site:

LogLevel debug filter:warn

I get log messages:
[Mon Jun 01 12:42:36.422149 2015] [:debug] [pid 12456:tid 140189141825280] filter.c(270): [client 176.8.83.57:47404] prefetching 65536 bytes, referer: http://host/servers/12591.html

I think, that is because filter does not report its 'module_name'

text: filter.c has nothing to do with mod_filter!
